			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Something Is Killing Saint Helena’s Cloud Forest</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">A deadly water mold—a relative of the pathogen that causes potato blight—is devastating what’s left of the South Atlantic island’s endemic trees.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/kevin-gepford/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Kevin Gepford</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						April 17, 2024 | 900 words, about 4 minutes
					</aside>

					
